    ‚Ä¢	Neglecting Responsibilities: Failing to fulfill work, school, or home responsibilities due to substance use.
    ‚Ä¢	Engaging in Risky Behaviors: Engaging in dangerous activities while under the influence, such as driving under the influence or unsafe sexual practices.
    ‚Ä¢	Social Withdrawal: Pulling away from friends, family, and social activities.
